{"tid":714841,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"想買全新suv5+2車，50萬內，有冇好介紹？？","createTime":"2018-06-24T03:18:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T07:02:21.000Z","uid":153391,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"0fe6e17532d316f60dfdf946b0a37d559d7c75b3","tid":714841,"uid":153391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T03:18:47.000Z","msg":"背景：揸左幾年1500cc車仔<br />\n因屋企開始多人，想換架大d既車<br />\n但一般只會在大時大節先要坐7人<br />\n又想要返d有少少操控性同馬力既<br />\n真7人車太大架（大食，無需要）<br />\nFreed, Sienta 呢d細7人車完全唔會諗<br />\n睇下咁多位高手有冇好既suv5+2介紹？<br />\n<br />\n我有留意開呢幾架：<br />\n1）BMW218i Gran Tourer7人版，睇過實物，但後排太dog seat，唔知仲有冇出1800/2000cc版（而家1500cc唔多吸引）<br />\n2）Nissan X-trail, 同上，都係後排太窄，同埋感覺好似好簿皮🙈<br />\n3）Honda CRV, 感覺上後排內籠好過上兩架<br />\n4）VW Tiguan Allspace, 未得閒去睇實物，感覺幾好<br />\n5) Mazada CX9 好似好正，但成五十幾個有d貴；CX5又好似冇7個位<br />\n<br />\n同埋掃把佬Forester幾時會有7人版？thx"},{"pid":"916feb70ea6bfbe6c204c396d0233b5efb5bf05c","tid":714841,"uid":52215,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T03:20:16.000Z","msg":"Kia Sorento柴油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddfd84b951609d6a1d0ca81163648effe2a831c0","tid":714841,"uid":91638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T05:11:18.000Z","msg":"Tiguan allspace 380 4motion <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5af3687b95975692c2140bbcfab1a9614e4a54c7","tid":714841,"uid":190817,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T05:30:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4tYTtWxKzrE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4tYTtWxKzrE&d=qGEn258Ii1sbyQSJeHwt0f9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=c6788e4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4tYTtWxKzrE</a><br />\nCX8同CX9 係咪一樣?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b467248f058b5ad1b6761810f6f94e032426c44","tid":714841,"uid":2346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":